@page "/privacy-policy"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<SeoComponent Title="@pageTitle"
    Description="Read Ítala Veloso Coaching's privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our coaching services and website."
    Keywords="privacy policy, data protection, personal information, GDPR compliance, privacy rights, data collection"
    CanonicalUrl="https://italaveloso.com/privacy-policy" RobotsContent="noindex, follow" />

<PageTitle>@pageTitle</PageTitle>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <div>
        <p>LAST UPDATED: 01/01/2025</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains
        how Ítala Veloso ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and shares information about you when you visit our website
        or use our services.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a
            href="mailto:jostic@italaveloso.com">jostic@italaveloso.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>2. Types of Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: Information that can identify you, such as your name, email, phone
            number, and job title.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Personal Information</strong>: Data that does not specifically identify you, like browsing
            behavior and device information.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Collect Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Directly from You</strong>: When you create an account, make a purchase, or contact us.</li>
        <li><strong>Automatically</strong>: Through cookies and similar technologies as you use our website.</li>
        <li><strong>From Third Parties</strong>: Information from partners or public sources.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide, personalize, and improve our services.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you regarding our services, updates, or promotions.</li>
        <li>Ensure the security and functionality of our website.</li>
        <li>Analyze trends and understand user behavior to enhance our offerings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share it with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers</strong>: Companies that help us deliver our services (e.g., hosting, analytics).
        </li>
        <li><strong>Business Partners</strong>: To offer joint promotions or services.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Requirements</strong>: When required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience. Cookies help us understand how you interact with our website and allow
        us to improve it. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, such as:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Access and Correction</strong>: You can request access to or correction of your personal data.</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion</strong>: You can ask us to delete your data when it's no longer needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Marketing Preferences</strong>: You can opt out of marketing communications at any time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Security Measures</h2>
    <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or
        disclosure. However, no system is 100% secure. If you suspect a breach, please contact us immediately.</p>

    <h2>9. Information from Children</h2>
    <p>Our services are not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from children. If
        you believe we have collected such information, please contact us so we can delete it.</p>

    <h2>10. International Data Transfers</h2>
    <p>We may transfer your information to countries outside your own. We ensure that appropriate safeguards are in
        place to protect your data.</p>

    <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on our website, and your continued use of our
        services signifies acceptance of those changes.</p>

    <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:jostic@italaveloso.com">jostic@italaveloso.com</a></li>
        <li>Address: 483 Green Lane, London, N13 4BS, United Kingdom</li>
    </ul>

</div>
